		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />2D is better than 3D - You and your 4th dimension -- it's cute! We have five. Thousand!
<br />
<br />Texture mapping on NES. Sounds like a fucking challenge. I did bumpmapping on GBC, gouraud shading and texture mapping on GBA (shipped titles). But never on an 8-bit-- that's *damn* interesting. If you say it's not possible or stupid, all you're saying is that you're not crazy enough, IMHO.

		

