		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'll be using rotation also, the best way I figure is to use the main feature of a NES cart.. having lots of memory.
<br />
<br />So instead of just this: <img src="http://www.parodius.com/~memblers/nes/jeep3bw.png" alt="Image" />
<br />
<br />Pre-calculate it all, and load it in the buffer.
<br /><img src="http://www.parodius.com/~memblers/nes/jeep3rot.png" alt="Image" />
<br />
<br />I think the program I used to generate that from the original graphic was Game Maker.

		

